---
description: Rules for FastAPI schemas and models
globs:
  - "backend/app/schemas/**/*.py"
  - "backend/app/models/**/*.py"
alwaysApply: false
---
- Use `schemas/` for Pydantic request and response contracts.
- Use `models/` for database or persistence models.
- Do not mix transport schemas and persistence models in the same file.
- Prefer explicit field types and clear naming.
